# Galactic Conquest: FAQ

Community-driven FAQ for **Galactic Conquest: Faction War**. This repo powers the in-game FAQ screen — every merged change goes live for all players.

## Contributing

We welcome contributions from the community. If you spot missing info, outdated answers, or have a question you think every new commander should see, open a pull request.

**Approved contributions earn you 300 Federal Crystals** deposited directly to your in-game account. Include your in-game username in the PR description so we can credit you.

## File Structure

All FAQ content lives in a single file: `faq.json`

The file contains a top-level `sections` array. Each section groups related questions under a heading.

## JSON Format

### Section

```json
{
  "title": "Section Name",
  "icon": "🚀",
  "items": []
}
```

- `title` — the section heading displayed in-game
- `icon` — a single emoji representing the section
- `items` — array of question/answer objects

### Item

```json
{
  "q": "Your question here?",
  "a": "Clear, concise answer here."
}
```

- `q` — the question as a player would ask it
- `a` — the answer, kept to a few sentences

### Full Example

Adding a new question to an existing section:

```json
{
  "q": "How does population cost scaling work?",
  "a": "Population uses tiered pricing — your first 120,000 pop costs 1 unit each, but every tier after that doubles the price. This keeps the economy balanced so high-population players can't snowball endlessly."
}
```

Add the object to the `items` array of the appropriate section in `faq.json`.

### Adding a New Section

If your questions don't fit any existing section, you can propose a new one:

```json
{
  "title": "Your Section Name",
  "icon": "🎯",
  "items": [
    {
      "q": "First question in the new section?",
      "a": "Answer here."
    }
  ]
}
```

Add the object to the `sections` array in `faq.json`.

## Current Sections

| Icon | Section | Topics |
|------|---------|--------|
| 🚀 | Getting Started | Fleets, home fleets, earning units |
| ⚔️ | Combat | Raiding, hacking, bombing, shields |
| 📋 | Contracts | PvE missions, troop management |
| 💎 | Economy & Items | Federal Crystals, Gems, population costs |
| 🏆 | Faction Orders | Events, Galactic Champion |
| ⚙️ | Account & Technical | Username changes, connectivity, Discord |

## PR Guidelines

1. Keep answers short and accurate — players skim, they don't read essays.
2. Write questions the way a player would actually ask them.
3. Validate your JSON before submitting. The file must parse cleanly or the PR will be rejected.
4. Place new items in the most relevant existing section before proposing a new one.
5. One topic per question — don't combine unrelated info into a single answer.

## Validation

Run this before submitting to make sure the JSON is valid:

```bash
python3 -c "import json; json.load(open('faq.json')); print('Valid')"
```

